chapter.para:
The big picture of this tutorial is illustrated in the figure below:
starting from an ecore metamodel;
we will provide editor to create its instance-model;
we will add contracts (through aspect weaving with Kermeta) to manage constraints specified inside the metamodel;
we will add some behaviour (through aspect weaving with Kermeta) where you can bind with another framework (provide GUI defined with another language - Java for example).
